#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:278
msgid "Settings to configure when messages are sent."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:281
msgid "Send messages on CTRL+ENTER"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:283
msgid ""
"If \"On for all messages\" is enabled, ENTER inserts a new line and "
"CTRL+ENTER posts a message. If \"On only for code blacks starting with "
"```\" is enabled, ENTER inserts a new line inside an open code block and "
"CTRL+ENTER automatically closes the code block and posts the message. If "
"disabled, SHIFT+ENTER inserts a new line and ENTER posts the message."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:286
msgid "Enable Post Formatting"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:288
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether post formatting is rendered. When \"On\", "
"posts will be rendered with `markdown formatting "
"<http://docs.mattermost.com/help/messaging/formatting-text.html>`__, "
"emoji, autolinked URLs, and line breaks. When \"Off\", the raw text will "
"be shown."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:291
msgid "Enable Join/Leave Messages"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:293
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether system messages about users joining or "
"leaving a channel are visible. When **On** these messages will appear. "
"When **Off**, these messages will be hidden. If any users are added to or"
" removed from a channel, a system message will still be shown even if "
"this setting is **Off**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:296
msgid "Preview pre-release features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:298
msgid ""
"Turn on preview features to view them early, ahead of their official "
"release:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:300
msgid ""
"**Show markdown preview option in message input box** Turning this on "
"will show a \"Preview\" option when typing in the text input box. "
"Pressing \"Preview\" shows what the Markdown formatting in the message "
"looks like before the message is sent."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:303
msgid "Deactivate Account"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/help/settings/account-settings.rst:305
msgid ""
"Use this setting to deactivate your account. After deactivating, an email"
